# Nothing required!
# claude_zoom shells out to `claude -p`, which reuses your existing
# Claude Code subscription auth. TTS is macOS `say` (built in). STT is
# Parakeet running locally via parakeet-mlx. No API keys needed.

# Optional tweaks for the `say` voice used in `claude-zoom present`:
# CLAUDE_ZOOM_SAY_VOICE=Samantha
# CLAUDE_ZOOM_SAY_RATE=180
